===Pronunciation===
עוף / ‛ôph / ofe

===Etymology===
From {{HH|5774}}; 

===Noun===
'''עוף'''

# A [[bird]] (as covered with feathers, or rather as covering with wings), often collective: - bird, that flieth, flying, [[fowl]].

